---
---

<section class="features-section" id="features">

  <!-- Section header: title left, desc + CTA right -->
  <div class="feat-header">
    <div class="feat-header-left">
      <span class="feat-tag">Features</span>
      <h2 class="feat-title">Todo lo que<br/>necesitas para<br/>producir más.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-header-right">
      <p>SubliFlow centraliza todo el flujo de producción de uniformes deportivos en una sola herramienta, conectada directamente con Adobe Illustrator.</p>
      <a href="#waitlist" class="btn btn-black">Ver todos los features →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Uniform 3-col card grid -->
  <div class="feat-grid">

    <div class="feat-card feat-dark">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Core</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">⚡</span>
      <h3>Reglas por talla,<br/>automáticas</h3>
      <p>Define una vez qué dimensiones y posiciones lleva cada pieza. SubliFlow lo aplica a cada jugador sin que tengas que pensar.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip white">S / M / L / XL / XXL</span>
        <span class="feat-chip white">Auto-dimensiones</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-card feat-yellow">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Flexible</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">👤</span>
      <h3>Overrides<br/>por jugador</h3>
      <p>¿Un jugador necesita algo diferente? Excepciones individuales sin romper las reglas generales del equipo.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Override individual</span>
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Sin romper reglas</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-card feat-light">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Import</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">📊</span>
      <h3>Importa desde<br/>Excel</h3>
      <p>Sube el roster en .xlsx. Nombre, número y talla de cada jugador se leen automáticamente.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Excel / .xlsx</span>
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Auto-parse</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-card feat-cyan">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Piezas</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">📐</span>
      <h3>4 piezas<br/>configurables</h3>
      <p>Frente, espalda, manga izq. y manga der. Cada una con sus propios elementos y reglas de escala.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Frente · Espalda</span>
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Manga Izq · Der</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-card feat-coral">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Illustrator</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">🔌</span>
      <h3>Plugin para<br/>Illustrator</h3>
      <p>El CSV exportado alimenta el plugin que genera todos los archivos listos para el plotter. Un clic.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip white">Plugin incluido</span>
        <span class="feat-chip white">Listo para ploter</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feat-card feat-light">
      <div class="feat-card-label">Organización</div>
      <span class="feat-emoji">📁</span>
      <h3>Múltiples<br/>equipos y clientes</h3>
      <p>Gestiona todos tus pedidos en un solo lugar. Cada cliente con sus propias reglas de diseño independientes.</p>
      <div class="feat-card-bottom">
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Equipos ilimitados</span>
        <span class="feat-chip dark">Multi-cliente</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    background: #FFFCF0;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
  }

  /* ─── Header ──────────────────────────── */
  .feat-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .feat-header-left {
    padding: 64px 48px;
    border-right: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    background: #00C8B8;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .feat-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    background: #0D0D0D;
    color: #00C8B8;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .feat-title {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    color: #0D0D0D;
  }

  .feat-header-right {
    padding: 64px 56px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .feat-header-right p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  /* ─── Uniform 3-col grid ──────────────── */
  .feat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    border-left: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
  }

  .feat-card {
    padding: 40px 36px;
    border-right: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .feat-card-label {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .feat-emoji {
    font-size: 44px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .feat-card h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .feat-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.75;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feat-card-bottom {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 2px solid currentColor;
    border-top-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .feat-chip {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 2px solid currentColor;
  }
  .feat-chip.white { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .feat-chip.dark  { color: rgba(13,13,13,0.5); }

  /* ─── Color themes ────────────────────── */
  .feat-dark {
    background: #0D0D0D;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .feat-dark .feat-card-label { color: #aaa; opacity: 1; }
  .feat-dark p { opacity: 0.6; }
  .feat-dark .feat-card-bottom { border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

  .feat-yellow {
    background: #FFE600;
    color: #0D0D0D;
  }

  .feat-light {
    background: #fff;
    color: #0D0D0D;
  }

  .feat-cyan {
    background: #00C8B8;
    color: #0D0D0D;
  }

  .feat-coral {
    background: #FF5757;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .feat-coral .feat-card-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); opacity: 1; }
  .feat-coral p { opacity: 0.85; }
  .feat-coral .feat-card-bottom { border-top-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }

  /* ─── Responsive ──────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .feat-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feat-header-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D; }
    .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .feat-header-left { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .feat-header-right { padding: 40px 24px; }
  }
</style>
